This is my cross platform vim settings
======================================

Major inspiration has been taken from http://amix.dk. thanks!

Install
-------
- Add this to the system's vimrc file
- Change the $1 to "mac", "linux" or "windows" depending on the system
- Update the paths.

fun! MySys()
   return "$1"
endfun

set runtimepath=~/.vim_runtime,~/.vim_runtime/after,\$VIMRUNTIME
source ~/.vim_runtime/vimrc
helptags ~/.vim_runtime/doc' > ~/.vimrc
